                <note rend="inline" type="source">741.5127/3a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-01-09T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 9, 1939—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>24. Department’s 13, January 6, 6 p.m., Antarctic. In a supplementary note please
                    request the appropriate authorities to be good enough to convey the contents of
                    your first note to His Majesty’s Governments in Australia and New Zealand.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
